definitions.definition: An irregular , jerky or awkward gait .
A scraper for removing poor ore or refuse from the sieve .

main_definition: An irregular , jerky or awkward gait .
secondary_definitions: A scraper for removing poor ore or refuse from the sieve .

definitions.definition: A scraper of board or sheet-iron shaped like half the head of a small cask, used for scraping the ore off the sieve in the operation of hand-jigging .

main_definition: A scraper of board or sheet-iron shaped like half the head of a small cask, used for scraping the ore off the sieve in the operation of hand-jigging .
